These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, bike, quad-bike, taxi, airplane, scooter, van
7 different pets are kept: rat, cat, bird, mouse, frog, rabbit, horse
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the owner of the horse is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the boat##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the horse##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is between the owner of the mouse and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
11. the person driving the scooter is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the owner of the rat is the person driving the airplane##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Transport   | boat  | taxi        | bike  | van     | scooter   | quad-bike       | airplane   |
| Pet         | cat   | horse | mouse    | bird  | frog | rabbit | rat |

