.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different pets are kept: pony, cat, frog, hamster, goldfish, guinea-pig, ferret
7 different games are played: go, chess, bridge, backgammon, poker, domino, scrabble
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, ship, train, trike
 1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person playing poker is the person playing poker##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person playing go is the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the owner of the pony is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the owner of the pony is between the person playing scrabble and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
12. the person driving the bus is the owner of the cat##1
13. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
14. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
16. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | ferret      | hamster     | pony  | goldfish | frog | cat |
| Game         | chess  | go | domino | bridge | scrabble | backgammon   | poker  |
| Transport     | roller   | train     | trike        | scooter  | ship   | car       | bus      |

