 2. the person who growsazalea is the journalist##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growsbellflower and the photographer##2
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the person who growszinnia is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
13. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in august##1
15. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
