.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, helicopter, skateboard, subway, train, van
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, cola, milk, fanta, coffee, sprite
There are 7 different nationalities: american, egyptian, french, indian, italian, mexican, turkish
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the french is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the mexican is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the american is the person driving the subway##1
11. the person drinking cola is the turkish##1
12. the person driving the trike is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking milk##2
15. the person driving the van is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Transport          | trike  | train    | subway  | jet-ski | skateboard  | van | helicopter |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola | sprite   | milk   | coffee | iced-tea     | 7up |
| Nationality   | italian | turkish   | american | french  | egyptian   | mexican    | indian    |

