 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the chinese##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the australian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 8. the person eating peach is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating radish##1
10. the person eating radish is the australian##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
12. the person eating grapes is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
13. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
14. the person eating cauliflower is the indian##1
15. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the australian##1
16. the person eating pomegranate is the french##1

