.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bolivar, montecristo, baccarat, dunhill, prince, blend
There are 7 different favourite colors: lilac, fuchsia, light-blue, coral, emerald, ebony, brown
 1. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is between the dunhill-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##2
 3. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the blend-smoker is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the prince-smoker##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 9. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes fuchsia##1
10. the writer is the person who likes emerald##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the blend-smoker is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
14. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Cigar   | blend | montecristo        | prince    | dunhill     | baccarat     | bolivar   | vegafina        |
| Color           | lilac   | light-blue       | ebony    | coral | emerald | brown   | fuchsia |

